Guguwar Rosa za ta kawo ruwan sama mai yawa a kudu maso yammacin Amirka
Kamar yadda aka annabta, guguwar Rosa tana raguwa yayin da take tafiya a kan ruwan sanyi a arewacin tekun Mexico.
