Rosa za ta kawo ruwan sama mai zurfi inci 10 a wasu wurare a ƙasar Mexico a ranar Litinin.
Bayan haka, zafin rana da ke kusa da iska mai sanyi zai iya kawo ruwan sama sosai a kudu maso yamma a kwanaki masu zuwa.
