An kiyasta cewa mutane fiye da miliyan 20.4 kamar yadda Nielsen ya ruwaito a ranar Jumma'a sun ga wannan ya faru.
Kamfanin yana lissafin yawan masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Wasu ƙididdigar ba su kasance nan take a kan wasu cibiyoyin sadarwa da suka nuna shirin ba, gami da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
