An yi wa Erdogan maraba da yawa a birnin Cologne
An yi murmushi da farin ciki a ranar Asabar (Satumba 29) lokacin da shugabannin Turkiyya da Jamus suka gana don karin kumallo a Berlin.
A yau ne ranar ƙarshe ta ziyarar Shugaba Erdogan zuwa Jamus - da nufin kyautata dangantaka tsakanin ƙasashen NATO.
Sun tattauna kan batutuwan da suka shafi 'yancin bil'adama, 'yancin' yan jarida da kuma shiga Turkiyya cikin EU.
Erdogan ya tafi Cologne don buɗe sabon babban masallacin.
A birnin, akwai 'yan ƙasar Turkiya da yawa da ba 'yan ƙasar Turkiya ba ne.
'Yan sanda sun yi amfani da dalilai na tsaro wajen hana taron mutane 25,000 su taru a gaban masallacin, amma magoya baya da yawa sun zo kusa don ganin shugaban su.
Daruruwan masu hamayya da Erdogan - da yawa daga cikinsu Kurdawa ne - sun yi magana, suna sūkar manufofin Erdogan da kuma shawarar da gwamnatin Jamus ta yanke na marabtarsa a ƙasar.
Wannan zane mai sassa biyu ya nuna bambancin ra'ayi game da wannan baƙo da wasu Turkawa na Jamus suke ɗaukan gwarzo ne kuma magabci ne mai zalunci ga wasu.
