MUKAMAN Mexico sun yi alkawarin cewa ba za su yi amfani da sojoji ba a kan farar hula
Zaɓaɓɓen shugaban ƙasar Mexico Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin cewa ba zai yi amfani da sojoji ba wajen yaƙi da farar hula yayin da ƙasar take gab da cika shekara 50 da kisan ɗalibai.
Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin ranar Asabar a Tlatelolco Plaza cewa "ba zai sake amfani da sojoji don zaluntar jama'ar Mexico ba".
Sojoji sun harbi ɗaliban da suke zanga-zangar lumana a filin a ranar 2 ga Oktoba, 1968, kuma sun kashe mutane kusan 300 a lokacin da ƙungiyoyin 'yancin kai na makaranta suka kafa a Latin Amirka.
Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin taimaka wa matasan Mexico ta hanyar ba da gudummawar kuɗi kowane wata ga waɗanda ke karatu da kuma buɗe jami'o'in gwamnati da yawa kyauta.
Ya ce rashin aikin yi da rashin ilimi suna sa matasa su shiga ƙungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda.
Gwamnatin Amirka ta ƙara kuɗin da za ta kashe don injina
Yayin da ƙasar Sin take samun ci gaba a fannin sarrafa kansa, Amirka tana bukatar ta ƙara saka kuɗi a bincike a wannan fannin, in ji Kai-Fu Lee, wani ɗan kasuwa da kuma mai son yin amfani da na'urorin sarrafa kansa, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft, da kuma Apple.
Wannan ya zo ne bayan da wasu sassan gwamnatin Amirka suka sanar da cewa za su yi amfani da wannan na'urar, yayin da ƙasar ba ta da tsarin AI mai tasiri.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta fara wannan shirin a bara: kuma tana da burin zama ta farko a amfani da wannan fasaha a shekarar 2030.
"Ƙara kuɗi don bincike zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, tun da dukan ƙasashe sun fi Amirka baya, kuma muna bukatar mu samu ayyuka masu ci gaba a wannan fannin", in ji Lee.
Wannan ƙarin kuɗin zai ninka damar samun nasara game da AI a cikin Amurka, Lee ya fada wa CNBC a cikin wata hira a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa "AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" aka buga a wannan watan da Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shugaban kamfanin Sinovation Ventures wanda ya zuba jari sosai a bincike kan na'urar sarrafa kansa a kasar Sin, Face++.
A shekara ta 1980, a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon, ya ƙirƙiri na'urar da ta yi nasara a wasan Othello kuma daga baya ya zama shugaban bincike a kamfanin Microsoft da kuma shugaban Google a ƙasar Sin.
Lee ya yi godiya ga ƙaddamar da gasar Robotics Challenge ta Hukumar Kula da Ayyukan Bincike na Tsaro kuma ya so sanin ranar da za a sake gudanar da gasar don taimakawa gano masu fasaha na gaba.
Lee ya ce, masu bincike a Amirka sau da yawa suna aiki tuƙuru don su sami lada daga gwamnati.
"Ba kasar Sin ba ce take karɓan masu ilimi; kamfanoni ne", in ji Lee.
