LeBron ya fara buga wa Lakers wasa a ranar Lahadi a San Diego
Masu sha'awar wasan sun yi jira don ganin LeBron James ya fara wasa a Los Angeles Lakers.
Kocin Lakers Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na kakar wasa a ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma ba a san yawan lokacin da za a yi wasan ba.
Walton ya ce a shafin yanar gizon Lakers: "Za su fi ɗaya kuma ƙasa da 48.
Mai ba da rahoto na Lakers Mike Trudell ya rubuta cewa James zai iya yin wasa na 'yan mintoci kaɗan.
Bayan wasan motsa jiki a farkon wannan makon, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na wasanni shida na kakar wasa ta Lakers".
