Bayan ta buga waƙarta ta uku ta Ghost Town a daren, inda ta saka hat da aka rubuta Make America Stronger, ta yi magana da ƙarfi ga 'yan jam'iyyar Democrat kuma ta sake cewa tana goyon bayan Trump.
"Sau da yawa ina magana da farar fata kuma suna cewa: "Me ya sa za ka so Mista Trump, shi ɗan wariyar launin fata ne?"
Don haka, idan na damu game da nuna bambanci da nuna bambanci, da na bar Amurka da dadewa", in ji ta.
SNL ta fara wasan kwaikwayon tare da Matt Damon lokacin da wannan ɗan wasan Hollywood ya yi ba'a da shaidar Brett Kavanaugh a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa game da zargin Christine Blasey Ford na fyade.
Kodayake ba a bayyana shi ba, an buga maganganun West a shafukan sada zumunta tare da Chris Rock mai ban dariya.
