Ko da yake ba a bayyana hujjojin Ford game da ƙoƙarin fyade na Kavanaugh ba, masana sun ce idan jam'iyyar Republican ta tabbatar da zaɓen Kavanaugh, za a yi fushi sosai.
"Wannan ya nuna rashin gaskiya na jam'iyyar Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National Committee, a makon da ya gabata, in ji rahoton NBC.
