Amma, jama'ar Amirka sun nuna bambancin ra'ayi game da wanda za su amince da shi bisa ga shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, kuma yawancin mutane suna goyon bayan Kavanaugh.
Wani sabon tsarin YoGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin dari na masu amsa sun amince da shaidar Ford, kuma kashi 35 cikin dari sun ce sun amince da shaidar Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce suna ganin cewa Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya, kuma kashi 30 cikin ɗari sun ce Ford ya yi ƙarya.
Bayan da aka ba da rahoton Flake, FBI na binciken batun da Ford da Deborah Ramirez suka bayar, in ji jaridar Guardian.
Ford da aka rantsar da shi ya ba da shaida a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar a makon da ya gabata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi ƙoƙari ya yi lalata da shi sa'ad da yake ɗan shekara 17.
Ramirez ya ce Kavanaugh ya nuna masa farjinsu a wani biki sa'ad da yake ɗalibi a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kafa dandalin Intane na Duniya Ɗaya yana son ya kafa dandalin Intane da zai yi gasa da Google da kuma Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro dandalin Intane na Duniya, yana son ya kafa dandalin da zai yi gasa da Facebook da Amazon da kuma Google.
Sabon aikin masanin, wanda ake kira Inrupt, wani kamfani ne da ke son ci gaba da aikin da aka dakatar da software mai ƙarfi wanda Berner-Lee ya sake tsarawa.
Shafin Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar yadda za su adana abubuwan da suke so kuma ya ba su damar zaɓar saƙon da suke so mutane su gani.
A wata hira ta musamman da jaridar Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wasa da cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "ta fi kowa".
"Dole ne mu yi haka yanzu", in ji shi game da shafin.
"Wannan labari ne mai kyau".
Wannan software za ta yi amfani da fasahar software ta Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar "yankin yanar gizo" na kansu ko POD.
Wannan shirin zai iya adana ayyuka, kalandarku, kiɗa, da kuma wasu abubuwa na sirri da na kasuwanci.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da kuma Spotify a lokaci ɗaya.
Wani abu na musamman game da wannan dandalin shi ne, mai amfani yana da 'yancin zaɓan waɗanda zai so su duba saƙon da yake so.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan shirin "taɗi mai ƙarfafawa".
Shugaban kamfanin, John Bruce ya ce manufarmu a Inrupt ita ce samar da kayayyaki, dabaru da fasahohi masu dacewa waɗanda za su sa kowa ya sami damar amfani da Solid.
Yanzu, wannan kamfani yana da Berners-Lee, Bruce, masu kula da tsaro da aka saya daga IBM, da kuma wasu masu aikin kwamfuta da aka ɗauke su aiki don su tsara tsarin, da kuma masu aikin sa kai da suka ƙware.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu fasaha a duniya suna iya yin amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt don tsara nasu software.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da abokan aikinsa ba sa tattaunawa da masu "Facebook da Google game da ko za su yi canje-canje na dindindin da za su sa a rufe dukan hanyoyin sadarwa na ɗan lokaci.
"Ba ma neman izini daga wurin su".
A cikin wani bayani da aka buga a shafin Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da ikon kasuwanci da tasirin muhalli don kare fasahar da ingancin sabon software daga Solid".
A shekara ta 1994 Berners-Lee ya kawo canji a yadda Intane ke aiki sa'ad da ya kafa dandalinsa na Intane, World Wide Web a makarantar kimiyya da fasaha da ke Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watanni da suka shige, Berners-Lee ya yi magana a kan batun haɗin gwiwar masu tsara Intane.
Ko da ya kafa Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da zama mai shi kuma darektan cibiyar yanar gizo ta duniya, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo da kuma Cibiyar Bayanai ta Buɗe.
"Ina da babban fata game da wannan sabon shirin", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: An yi wa wani limami da ya sami Victoria Cross bayan ya yi yaƙi a yaƙin duniya na farko na WW1 yabo
Limamin Cocin Ingila da ya sami Gicciye ta Victoria a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na biyu a matsayin soja ya ci gaba da yin farin ciki a garinsu har bayan shekara ɗari.
Limamin Lt. Col. Bernard Vann ya gano wannan tauraron a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, a lokacin da aka yi yaƙi a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Amma, bayan kwana huɗu, wani ɗan soja ya kashe shi, ba tare da sanin cewa ya sami matsayi mafi girma a rundunar sojojin Biritaniya ba.
