Taron rediyo na Desert Island: Tom Daley ya 'ɓoye kansa' game da ƙungiyar da yake so
Wani ɗan wasa mai tsalle-tsalle a gasar Olympics ya girma yana ɓoye kansa daga rukunin da yake ƙauna.
Wannan mai shekaru 24 da haihuwa ya ce bai fahimci cewa "kowa ba kamarsa ba ne" ba sai da ya shiga makarantar sakandare.
A wani jawabi da Lauren Laverne ta yi a shirin farko na hira guda huɗu a gidan rediyon Desert Island, ta ce tana magana game da 'yancin 'yan luwadi don ta ba wasu "bege".
Ya kuma ce yin renon yara ya hana shi yin tunani game da yadda zai yi nasara a wasanni.
Kirsty Young, mai gabatar da shirin, ta yi watanni da yawa ba ta halarci taron ba don rashin lafiya.
Da yake jawabi a shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya ce tun yana ƙarami yana ganin kansa "marasa amfani" domin "ba a yarda da sha'awar maza da mata ba".
Ya ce: "Har wa yau, jin na fi sauran mutane da kuma kasancewa dabam da wasu abubuwa ne da suke ƙarfafa ni da kuma ƙarfafa ni in yi nasara a wasanni".
Yana son ya nuna wa mutane cewa shi "na Allah ne", in ji shi, don kada ya ɓata wa kowa rai idan ya san cewa yana son wasu mutane.
Wannan mai lashe lambar tagulla sau biyu a gasar ya zama sanannen mai fafutukar kare hakkin 'yan luwadi kuma ya yi amfani da halartarsa a wasannin Commonwealth a Ostiraliya a wannan shekara don yin kira ga ƙasashe da yawa don yin doka game da auren jinsi ɗaya.
Ya ce yana magana ne domin yana jin cewa yana da gata ya kasance da 'yanci duk da cewa ya furta ƙaunarsa ga 'yan'uwansa kuma yana son ya ba da "ƙarfafawa" ga wasu.
Wannan mai cin kofin duniya sau uku ya ce, "na yi mamaki sosai" sa'ad da ta soma soyayya da wani ɗan fim ɗan Amirka mai suna Dustin Lance Black, wanda ta haɗu da shi a shekara ta 2013.
Daley ta auri ɗan fim ɗin, wanda ya lashe lambar yabo ta Oscar, shekara 20 da ta shige a shekarar da ta shige amma ta ce bambancin ba shi da muhimmanci.
"Idan ka fuskanci abubuwa da yawa a wannan shekarun"  ta shiga gasar Olympics sa'ad da take 'yar shekara 14 kuma mahaifinta ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka - ta ce yana da wuya a sami mutumin da ya fuskanci matsalolin da ta fuskanta.
A watan Yuni, ma'auratan suka haifi ɗa mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma Daley ya ce "ra'ayinsu" ya canja.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, zan yi tunanin lashe lambar zinariya", in ji shi.
"Amma ka sani, akwai abubuwa da yawa da suka fi lambar zinariya a gasar Olympics muhimmanci.
Robbie ne zinariyar da na samu a gasar Olympics".
An ba wa ɗanta sunan mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana ɗan shekara 40 bayan da aka gano cewa yana da ciwon daji a ƙwaƙwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda cewa yana mutuwa ba kuma abin da ya yi tambaya kafin mutuwarsa shi ne ko an samu tikitin zuwa gasar London ta 2012 - domin yana son ya zauna a gaba.
"Ba zan gaya musu cewa ba za ku kasance a gaba ba domin za ku mutu", in ji shi.
"Na riƙe hannunsa sa'ad da yake mutuwa, kuma sa'ad da ya mutu ne na fahimci cewa ba ya dawwama", in ji shi.
A shekara ta gaba, Daley ya yi tsere a gasar Olympics ta shekara ta 2012 kuma ya ci lambar tagulla.
"Na san cewa wannan ne burina - in yi iyo a gaban jama'a a gasar Olympics, kuma babu abin da ya fi wannan", in ji shi.
Wannan ya ƙarfafa zaɓinta na farko na waƙa - Proud na Heather Small - wadda ta ƙarfafa ta a lokacin da take shirin gasar Olympics kuma har ila tana ƙarfafa ta.
