An kori Mickelson daga gasar cin kofin Ryder a ranar Asabar
Phil Mickelson na Amirka ya kafa tarihi a wasan Ryder Cup na 47 da ya buga a ranar Lahadi, amma zai yi wasa fiye da yadda yake yi a dā don ya ci gaba da yin wasa.
Mickelson, wanda ya buga wasan na 12 a gasar a cikin shekaru biyu, an cire shi kuma ya maye gurbinsa da mai kula da 'yan wasa, Jim Furyk a wasan hudu da hudu.
Maimakon ya zama ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasan a ranar, kamar yadda yake yi a dā, wannan ɗan wasan da ya lashe gasar cin kofin Amirka sau biyar yana ta murna da abokansa kuma yana yin shiri don ya ci gaba da yin wasa.
Wannan ɗan wasan mai shekara 48 wanda ba shi da haɗari sosai a lokacin da yake ƙwallon ƙafa, ba shi da ƙwarewa a gasar Le Golf National da ake buga ƙwallon ƙafa a nesa.
Idan ba a yi wasa ba, Mickelson zai yi wasa na tara a ranar Lahadi da Francesco Molinari, ɗan wasan ƙwallon ƙafa na ƙasar Biritaniya, wanda ya yi wasa da Tommy Fleetwood, wanda shi ne ɗan wasa na farko da ya ci wasanni huɗu a wannan makon.
Idan 'yan wasan Amirka, da suka rage maki huɗu a wasan farko na wasanni 12, suka yi nasara, wasan Mickelson zai zama da muhimmanci.
Furyk ya ce ya amince da wannan masani, amma bai faɗa kome ba.
Furyk ya ce: "Ya fahimci abin da ya kamata ya yi a yau, ya yaba mini kuma ya rungume ni kuma ya gaya mini cewa za su kasance a shirye don wasannin gobe.
"Yana da son kai.
Shi ne babban gwani kuma ya yi wa tawagar aiki sosai a baya, har ma a wannan makon.
Ba na tsammanin zai yi wasa biyu.
Ina sa rai cewa zai yi wasa sosai, amma hakan ya faru kuma mun yi abin da ya kamata.
Yana son ya yi wasa kamar kowa".
A wasannin da ake yi a ranar Lahadi, Mickleson ya ci Nick Faldo a yawan wasannin da ake yi a gasar Ryder.
Hakan zai sa ya yi wasa da kansa a wani yanayi dabam da na sa'ad da yake wasa da kansa.
Mickelson ya ci 18, ya sha kashi 20, kuma ya yi wasa guda bakwai, amma Furyk ya ce kasancewa a wurin yana ƙarfafa tawagarsa.
"Yana da fara'a, yana da fara'a, yana da fara'a, yana son mutane, kuma mutum ne mai kyau da za a zauna da shi", in ji ta.
"Ina ganin matasa 'yan wasa sun yi farin ciki da suka yi wasa da shi, a wannan makon, abin farin ciki ne a gani.
Yana ba da fiye da wasa".
Shugaban 'yan wasan Turai Thomas Bjorn ya san cewa za a iya halaka matsayinsu na shugabanci
Thomas Bjorn ya sani daga abin da ya faru a dā cewa ci gabansa a gasar Ryder Cup zai iya zama abin da ba zai yiwu ba.
Dan wasan Denmark ya yi wasan farko a Valderrama a shekara ta 1999, inda ƙungiyarsa mai suna Seve Ballesteros ta ci gaba da ci gaba da maki biyar a kan Amirka amma ta ci nasara da ƙarancin maki 141⁄2 da 131⁄2.
"Na tunatar da kaina cewa muna da babban jagoranci a Valderrama; muna da babban jagoranci a Brookline, inda muka rasa, kuma a Valderrama inda muka ci nasara, amma da karancin maki", in ji Bjorn, bayan kallon mafi kyawun ƙungiyar a 2018 ta ci 5-3 a ranar Juma'a da jiya don samun ci gaba 10-6 a gasar Le Golf National.
Saboda haka tarihi ya koya mini da kuma kowa a cikin wannan rukunin cewa wasan ba ya ƙare.
Muna bukatar mu ci gaba da yin hakan.
Bari mu je gidan wasan kwaikwayo kuma mu yi kyau.
Mun ci gaba da yin wasan har sai mun ci kwallo.
Muna da maƙasudin yin ƙoƙari mu ci kofin kuma wannan ne ya kamata mu mai da hankali a kai.
Na sha cewa ina son 'yan wasa 12 da ke cikin tawagarmu, kuma mun san 'yan wasan da muke wasa da su - 'yan wasa mafi kyau a duniya".
Bjorn ya yi farin ciki da yadda 'yan wasansa suka yi wasa a filin golf mai wuya, ya ce: "Ba na jin kaɗaici.
Wasannin gobe suna da yawa.
Kowa zai iya yin abin da ya fi ƙarfinsa, kuma hakan yana da wuya.
Yin wasa da abokin tarayya yana da kyau idan abubuwa suna tafiya daidai, amma yin wasa da kanka, kamar masu wasan golf, gwaji ne na gaske.
Sakon da ya kamata ya ba 'yan wasan shi ne su nuna halin namiji a wasannin gobe.
A nan, ka bar abokin wasan ka kuma ya sake yin aikinsa".
Jim Furyk zai bukaci 'yan wasansa su yi aiki tuƙuru fiye da yadda suke yi a rukuni biyu, ban da Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas da suka ci uku cikin huɗu.
Furyk da kansa ya kasance a ɓangarorin biyu na canji, ya kasance a cikin tawagar da ta yi nasara a Brookline kafin ya zama tawagar da ta yi rashin nasara sa'ad da tawagar Turai ta "yi mu'ujizai" a Medinah".
"Na tuna da kome", in ji shi sa'ad da aka tambaye shi yadda Ben Crenshaw, shugaban 'yan wasa na shekara ta 1999 ya ƙarfafa 'yan wasansa a ranar ƙarshe ta wasan.
"Muna da wasanni 12 masu muhimmanci amma dole ne mu tashi da wuri kamar yadda kuka gani a Brookline da kuma Medinah.
Idan hakan ya faru, masu wasan tsakiya suna cikin matsi.
