An harbe mutum da bindiga a Ilfracombe
Wani mutum ya ji harbi da bindiga sau da yawa sa'ad da yake dawowa gida daga wurin da ya kwana.
Wanda aka kashe, wanda ke cikin shekarunsa na 40, yana yankin Oxford Grove a Ilfracombe, Devon, lokacin da aka harbe shi a kirji, ciki da hannu.
'Yan sanda sun bayyana harbin, wanda ya faru da misalin karfe 2:30 na yammacin Amurka, a matsayin "ba tare da gangan ba".
Wanda aka harba bai san wanda yake harbi ba.
Raunukansa ba su da tsanani kuma 'yan sanda sun nemi taimako daga duk wanda ya ga abin da ya faru.
Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne girgizar ƙasa da tsunami mai ƙarfi da ta auku a birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Jumma'a suka kashe, in ji hukumomi, kuma ana sa ran adadin mutuwar zai ƙaru.
Saboda lalacewar hanyar sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun bayanai daga yankin Donggala ba, yankin arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga wurin da bala'in ya auku.
Ga wasu bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birni ne a lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, wanda ke ƙarshen wani ƙaramin kwarin bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda ke da mazaunan kusan 379,800 a shekara ta 2017.
A ranar ne aka yi bikin cika shekara 40 da girgizar ƙasar ta auku.
Donggala yanki ne da ke da nisan mil 300 (180 miles) a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A shekara ta 2017, mazaunan wannan yanki sun kai 299,200.
Kamfanonin kamun kifi da noma suna da muhimmanci ga tattalin arzikin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, musamman yankin Donggala.
Ana kuma haƙa nickel a wannan yankin, amma ana samunsa sosai a Morowali, wani bakin teku da ke gefen Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta ƙasar Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, an yi tsunami da yawa a Palu da Donggala.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala
Wani tsunami kuma ya auku a yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, ya kashe mutane tara.
Kasar Indonesia tana cikin yankin Pacific Risk Zone kuma ana yawan samun girgizar ƙasa.
Ga jerin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da aka yi a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi da ta auku a yammacin bakin teku na yankin Aceh a ƙasar Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta jawo tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gaɓar Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin mutanen Aceh.
2005: An yi wata girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta auku a kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, wanda ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya mamaye gabar kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta auku a birnin Padang, babban birnin Yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, kusa da Sumatra, kuma ta haddasa tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani karamin girgizar kasa ya afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ya haifar da barna da tsoro yayin da mutane ke tunawa da girgizar kasa da tsunami da suka yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane da yawa a 2004.
Babu tsunami da ya faru a wannan lokacin, amma fiye da 100 sun mutu a lokacin da gidaje suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin yawon buɗe ido na Lombok a Indonesia, ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gidaje kuma ta sa dubban baƙi su sha wahala na ɗan lokaci.
An Kama Ɗan Sarah Palin na Dā a Kan Laifin Mugunta a Iyalinsa
Track Palin, ɗan fari na tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, an kama shi da laifin cin zarafi.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, saboda aikata laifin cin zarafin iyali, da kuma ƙin yin shari'a, a cewar rahoton da 'yan sanda na jihar Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
Wani rahoto ya nuna cewa wata mata ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran 'yan sanda don ta gaya musu game da wannan laifin, amma suka ƙwace wayar daga hannun ta.
An tsare Palin a gidan yarin Mat-Su Pretrial Facility kuma an tsare shi a kan belin da ba shi da tsaro na $ 500, in ji KTUU.
Ya bayyana a kotu a ranar Asabar, inda ya ce "ba shi da laifi, gaskiya" lokacin da aka tambaye shi, in ji cibiyar sadarwa.
Ana tuhumar Palin da laifuffuka uku na Class A, wanda ke nufin cewa za a iya yanke masa hukuncin ɗaurin shekara guda da kuma tara dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin Class B, wanda ake yankewa hukuncin ɗaurin kwana ɗaya da tara $ 2,000.
Wannan ba shi ne karo na farko da aka kai Palin kotu ba.
A watan Disamba na 2017, an zarge shi da cin zarafin mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
