A watan Janairun 2016 an zarge shi da aikata laifin tashin hankali a cikin gida, da lalata rahoton shari'ar da kuma mallakar makami yayin da yake cikin maye.
Yarinyar ta ce an buge ta a fuska.
A shekara ta 2016 Sarah Palin ta fuskanci zargi daga manyan sojoji bayan ta danganta batun cin zarafin ɗanta da PTSD wanda ta ce ya faru ne saboda aikinta a matsayin soja a Iraki.
