Masu shari'a na tarayya suna neman waɗanda ake zargi da ta'addanci a NYC don yanke hukuncin kisa na ban mamaki
Alƙalai a Birnin New York suna son a yanke wa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, domin an zarge shi da aikata ta'addanci a NYC kuma ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taɓa yankewa ba tun shekara ta 1953.
An ce Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya daga Home Depot don yin ta'addanci a kan hanyar keke kusa da babbar hanyar West Side a Lower Manhattan, inda ya kashe masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu keke a cikin watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, dole ne masu shari'a su ba da tabbacin cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas "da gangan" kuma ya "da gangan" ya ji wa wasu rauni, a cewar dokar da aka gabatar a Kotun Kudancin New York.
An yi wa waɗannan laifuffukan duka hukuncin kisa, kamar yadda aka rubuta a cikin takardar kotu.
Bayan an yi makonni da yawa ana shari'a, babban kotun ya yanke wa Saipov hukunci a kan tuhume-tuhume 22 da suka haɗa da tuhume-tuhume takwas na kisan kai da aka yi da gangan, da kuma tuhume-tuhume na yin faɗa da kuma lalata mota.
Alkalin kotun ya ce "an shirya shari'ar sosai kuma an yi la'akari da ita sosai", in ji alƙalai, suna mai bayyana yadda Saipov ya yi "matsananci, zalunci da mummunan hali".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya cutar da wasu, kuma ya jawo baƙin ciki ga dangi da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", in ji karar da aka yanke a baya.
Biyar cikin waɗanda aka kashe baƙi ne daga ƙasar Ajantina.
Shekara goma ke nan tun lokacin da Kotun Kudancin New York ta yanke hukuncin kisa.
An samu wanda aka yanke masa hukuncin kisa, Khalid Barnes, da laifin kashe wasu masu fataucin miyagun kwayoyi biyu amma daga karshe aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekara ta 1953 ne aka yanke hukuncin kisa a birnin New York a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin yin leken asiri ga gwamnatin Soviet a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe ma'aurata na iyalin Rosenberg da kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin damuwa game da ayyukansa a cikin kwanaki da watanni masu zuwa, a cewar takardun kotu.
Ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗin abin da ya yi, in ji 'yan sanda.
Saipov ya shaida wa jami'an cewa an tilasta masa yin hakan ne bayan da ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, a cewar bayanan da ke cikin shari'arsa.
Har ma ya nemi a nuna tutar ISIS a ɗakinsa na asibiti, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya ƙi zargin da aka yi masa na 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin wakilan Saipov, ya ce "ya yi takaici" da shawarar da alƙalan tarayya suka yanke.
"Muna ganin cewa shawarar da za a ba da hukuncin kisa maimakon a ba da damar da za a ci gaba da ɗaurin kurkuku ba tare da samun damar samun 'yanci ba zai ƙara baƙin ciki ga kowa da ke ciki", in ji Patton.
Lauyoyin Saipov sun riga sun roƙi alƙalai su ƙyale hukuncin kisa.
'Yan majalisa sun ce NIGEL FARAGE ya kamata ya jagoranci tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin cewa zai 'kira jama'a su yi yaƙi' a yau a wani zanga-zanga a taron 'yan majalisa.
Tsohon shugaban Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa su 'yi ƙoƙari' su yi magana da 'yan adawa da EU - kamar yadda ɗaya daga cikin masu ba Theresa May shawara ya ce ya dace a yi magana da EU.
Peter Bone, wanda ya koma baya, ya shaida wa jama'a a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya 'da ta fita' a yanzu idan Farage ne Sakataren tattaunawar Brexit.
Amma matsalar da Mrs May ke fuskanta wajen dawo da yankunan da aka raba su sosai an tabbatar da ita ta hanyar 'Yan adawa da Brexit don shiga wasu zanga-zangar adawa da Brexit a cikin birni.
Shugaban yana ƙoƙarin inganta shirinsa na ba da izini ga masu goyon bayan Brexit, masu neman zama a cikin EU da kuma EU.
Abokan aikinsa sun nace cewa za su ci gaba da ƙoƙarin yin yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da hamayya - kuma su tilasta wa 'yan adawa da EU da ma'aikatan jam'iyyar su zaɓi tsakanin abin da suke bayarwa da 'rikice-rikice'.
Mista Bone ya shaida wa wani taron da ake kira 'Barin ya nuna Barin Solihull' cewa yana son 'zartar da ƙarar ƙin amincewa da yarjejeniyar Brexit'.
Ya kuma ce Farage zai shiga cikin tattaunawar da za a yi da Brussels.
'Da a ce shi ne yake ja-gorar batun, da mun fita yanzu,' in ji shi.
'Zan goyi bayan Brexit amma muna so mu yi tir da masu adawa da yarjejeniyar Brexit,' in ji dan majalisa na Wellingborough.
Da yake nuna rashin amincewarsa da EU, ya ce: 'Ba mu yi yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya don mu zama bayi ba.
Muna son mu kafa dokokinmu a ƙasarmu.'
Bone ya musanta cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun lokacin zaben 2016: 'Ba gaskiya ba ne cewa mutanen Burtaniya sun canza ra'ayinsu kuma suna son ci gaba.'
Andrea Jenkyns, wadda ta amince da barin ƙasar Ingila, ita ma tana wajen, ta gaya wa 'yan jarida: 'Ina cewa: Firayim Minista, ku saurari mutane.
'Babu bukatar zama a cikin EU, 'Yan adawa ba za su yarda da wannan ba, ba ma bukatar jam'iyyarmu da masu gwagwarmayar da muke gwagwarmaya da su don zaɓe.
Don Allah ku bar EU kuma ku soma sauraron mutane.'
Ga Mrs. May, ta daɗa: 'Manyan mutane kamar firaminista suna cika aikinsu idan sun cika alkawuransu.'
Farage ya gaya wa masu sauraro a taron cewa dole ne a 'tilasta' 'yan siyasa idan ba su da gaskiya ga zaben 2016.
Yanzu batun da ke tsakaninmu ne - mutane - da kuma jam'iyyarmu ta siyasa,' in ji shi.
'Suna ƙoƙarin cin amana game da Brexit kuma muna nan a yau don gaya musu 'ba za mu bar ku ku yi hakan ba'.'
